name: Super Mullet electric guitar strings
description:
Like the perfect mullet, these electric strings need no introduction! Constructed of ultra-high tensile hexagon cores with precision-spun premium nickel alloy. Super Mullets are packed with killer tone, punch and durability. Extended playing time may result in a deeper sense of appreciation and kinship with the mullet world. All Super Mullet sets include an extra high-E string.

name: Red Headed Acoustic Guitar Strings
description:
Raised in the Knucklehead Family, this is one redheaded stepchild you’ll love to pick on! These premium acoustic strings are made of ultra-high tensile hexagon cores and precision-spun rare phosphor bronze alloy. Redheaded Stepchilds produce the most brilliant, warm, balanced tone you will find anywhere. All Redheaded Stepchild sets come with an extra high-E string (12-string / extra high-G.)

name: Doublewide Electric Bass Strings
description:
These high in calorie bass strings are loaded with all the fatness and girth you can handle! Doublewides are crafted of ultra-high tensile hexagon cores with precision-spun premium nickel alloy. You can expect nothing less than huge tone and incredible punch that will give you that warm fuzzy feeling deep inside.

name: Combover Classical Guitar Strings
description:
Unlike the comb-over, these classical strings have absolutely nothing to hide! Crafted of precision wound silver-plated copper and clear nylon trebles, Combovers give remarkable depth and crystal clear tone. These balanced and durable strings will withstand any strong windstorm.

name: Short Bus Custom Electric Guitar Strings
description:
Some of us have needs that require a little extra love and special attention. ShortBus sets are built with ultra-high tensile hexagon cores and precision-spun nickel alloy. Although you might need to come a little later and leave a little earlier, don’t worry you will not miss a thing. These strings will take you to the deepest of tone and lowness. ShortBus will definitely satisfy all your special needs. All ShortBus sets include an extra high-E string.
